							<br>
							<h2>Hunger of the World: a Table Grace</h2>
							<b>Voicing:</b> flexible, 1-8 part canon, a cappella<br>
							<b>Text:</b> Josephine Preston Peabody (1903)<br>
							<b>Language:</b> English<br>
							<b>Duration:</b> varies<br>
							<b>Commissioned by:</b> Empty Bowls Project at Independent School District #191, Minn.<br>
							<b>Premiere date:</b> Thursday, October 25, 2007<br>
							<b>Premiered by:</b> Combined elementary school choirs, Ind. District 191, Burnsville, MN<br>
							<b>Published by:</b> Abbie Betinis Music Co., AB-050-03<br>
							<b>Order online:</b> <a href="../order_form.html">Online order form</a><br>
							<br>
							<br>
							<span class="works-headers">PROGRAMMING SUGGESTIONS</span>
							<div class="works-body">
							* World Food Day (annually on October 16).  <a href="http://www.fao.org/world-food-day" target="blank">Learn more at United Nations</a>.<br>
							* Sing in conjunction with, or <a href="https://www.thekitchn.com/how-to-host-an-empty-bowls-fundraiser-to-fight-hunger-237200" target="blank">learn how to host an Empty Bowls event</a> to help fight hunger in your community.<br>
							* Get the latest <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=hunger+statistics">world hunger statistics</a>.<br>
							</div><br>
							
